raw.name: Rudiger
raw.bio: Ugh! I'm Rudiger. I believe that one day cats will rule this planet. I put marmalade on everything. Like, everything: hot dogs, ice creamâ€”everything! Let's pawty!
Shalom! I'm Kitty #200000. I've never told anyone this, but I once loved a dog. I once got in a fight with a rhino, and won. Can't wait to eat apple pie with you!
Uh, hi! I'm Kitty #300000. I'm a Train Conductor by day, and I like siring for status by night. Some people say I'm the Dwight Schrute of the group. In time you'll learn how purrfect I am.

Hi-ya! I'm Kitty #400000. I'm a Aerobics Athlete  by day, and I like mocking dogs by night. It wasn't heavily publicized, but I once had a brief relationship with Stimpy. I look forward to chasing red dots with you.

raw.name: Milestone Kitty #700000
raw.bio: Yaya. My name is Milestone Kitty #700000. I can't wait to hear all about your favourite condiments! Mine are dijon mustard and mayonnaise. If you want to join me and my clique, you should know that on Wednesdays we wear pink. Are you a magician? Because whenever I look at you, everyone else disappears!

*winces*. My name is Kitty #800000. I have no idea how I got here, but I know it involves blazers and a fairy. I like to tell stories, which are often either lawful or exuberant. Are you a parking ticket? â€˜Cause youâ€™ve got fine written all over you.

raw.name: Kitty 900000
raw.bio: Aloha, my name is Kitty 900000, but you can call me whatever you like *wink*. In another life, I think I would have been a goose. What's that smell?

raw.name: Vulcat
raw.bio: A toast in your honour, my friend. I'm Vulcat. Some people like to do things right, but I prefer them well done. A wise man once told me that if you build a person a fire, they'll be warm for a day. It turns out that if you set a wise man on fire, they'll be warm for the rest of their life.
